# Exclude all _site EXCEPT tool-recommend pages (which are pre-built)
_site/*
!_site/tool-recommend/
_site/tool-recommend/*
!_site/tool-recommend/product-1/
!_site/tool-recommend/product-1/**/*
!_site/tool-recommend/product-2/
!_site/tool-recommend/product-2/**/*
